title: Beyond the Horror: Apocalypse Episode 9
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Kenny said, “negative Nancy!?” I love him even more for that. Carry on. ☮️
Didn't anybody else notice that Venable never wore "Dental Appliances"? It's like they scrapped some ideas before it was discovered to be the crossover.
Dinah did look like she felt bad, after she really looked at the slaughter, you could see the guilt on her face.
I think Michael was like a whiny teenager prior to the Cooperative getting a hold of him...then we get the powerful, self assured Michael we see at the beginning of the series.
Mary you should do a break down of next weeks trailer. That would be Awesome!!!! 😉👊👍🤪🤟
